<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>rby ạʿṭny nwr wjhk</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- rby ạʿṭny nwr wjhk
 ạstnyr fy ạlẓlạm
 wạmlạn ḥyạty bḥbk
 wạsẖmlny bạlslạm

[V2]
 ạlqrạr: fy ṭryq ạljljtẖẗ ạ̉syr
 qạṣdạ nḥw ạlṣlyb
 fạhdny ạlyk yạ qdyr
 wạjdẖbny yạ ḥbyb

[V3]
 2- ldẖty ạ̉nạ fy ḥdytẖk
 ḥdtẖny kl ận
 bhjty hnạ fy rḥạbk
 ạsknny dẖạ ạlmkạn

[V4]
 3- ạ̹n ly ạsẖtyạq ạ̉n ạry̱ snạk
 ḥqqn dẖạ ạlrjạʾ
 wạskbn ly mn gẖny̱ smạk
 rwḥ qds llʿzạʾ

[V5]
 4- ạḥfẓn kẖṭạy rby ạlʿly
 ạrsẖdny fy ạlṭryq
 qdsny fy ḥqk ạljly
 kn ṣdyqy wạlrfyq</lyrics>
